COMPILE EVALUATE_BUFFER ~ahungry_heart/dialogues/uxbana25.d~  // All Branwen's ToB banters with other party members will go here. Again, we use 25, because it's a tradution for ToB. Again, "EVALUATE_BUFFER" because of the chapter numbers
